data.message: Polish MSJ spacing and visual consistency: Tightened spacing across all 5 pages and 4 components. Established consistent spacing system: pt-6 headers, px-5 horizontal padding, p-4 cards, py-3.5 list items. Reduced typography sizes slightly for better mobile proportions. Fixed TabBar to bottom with gradient fade. App now feels cohesive and polished.
